headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Buy and Hold Forever
summary: Unfortunately, many companies will, at some point, have to resort to dividend cuts because of business challenges.  Visa, a leading payment network company, has an excellent dividend track record.  Visa can afford it: It generates consistent and growing revenue, earnings, and free cash flow.
